      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. SYCAMORE SHORTY is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 23.36 beating Bianca's Secret. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Hard to go past. 7. PAW YUSAMI was game in defeat with a narrow loss in last time, when a nose second behind Shifty Bulldozer in 22.85 and posting a new PB this course and distance. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. 8. PAY TIME has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (18.86) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can hit the frame this time. 2. MUDDY DUCK is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.\",\"runners\":[1,7,8,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
